id: pm-kj4k
title: "GH-530: list --status <invalid> silently returns count 0 — validate against the status domain like --type and search status:"
description: "pm list --status bogusstatus returns count:0 exit 0 while pm list --type BogusType and pm search 'x' status:notarealstatus both fail fast with the valid domain. An agent reading the empty result concludes 'no matching items' — silent-wrong-data class, sibling of pm-96vo (GH-526 aggregate --sum/--avg silent 0 on unknown fields). Fix: validate --status against open|closed|canceled + configured status ids (same validator search uses) and error with the domain list; sweep other list filters (--assignee? --tag?) for the same fail-fast gap at fix time so the filter surface is uniformly validated."
type: Issue
